Name: Percentage of 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' out of all activity executions in the event log
Metric: Percentage of 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' out of all cases

Name: Frequency of 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' occurrences across all cases
Metric: Number of 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' activities

Name: Percentage of process variants that include 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor'
Metric: Percentage of 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' out of all cases

Name: Frequency of 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' followed by 'Completed + Resolved'
Metric: Number of 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' activities for cases where activity 'Completed + Resolved' occurs

Name: Percentage of 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' that occurs after 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment'
Metric: Percentage of 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' out of all 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment'

Name: Ratio of 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' to 'Accepted + Wait - User' in the entire log
Metric: Percentage of 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' out of all 'Accepted + Wait - User'

Name: Number of times 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' appears in variants with total performance duration above 1,000,000 time units
Metric: Number of 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' activities

Name: Percentage of cases containing 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' that eventually reach 'Completed + Closed'
Metric: Percentage of 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' out of all 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Frequency of 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' compared to the frequency of 'Completed + In Call'
Metric: Number of 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' activities for cases where activity 'Completed + In Call' occurs

Name: Percentage of 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' occurrences relative to all 'Accepted + Wait' type activities (including 'Accepted + Wait', 'Accepted + Wait - User', 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation', and 'Accepted + Wait - Customer')
Metric: Percentage of 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' out of all 'Accepted + Wait'

Name: Number of distinct process variants where 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' is immediately preceded by 'Accepted + In Progress'
Metric: Number of 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' activities for cases where activity 'Accepted + In Progress' occurs

Name: Percentage of 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' events that occur in cases also containing 'Completed + In Call'
Metric: Percentage of 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' out of all 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Frequency of transitions from 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' directly to 'Completed + Resolved'
Metric: Number of 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' activities for cases where activity 'Completed + Resolved' occurs

Name: Percentage of all 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' instances that appear only once per case
Metric: the average of the function base == 1 where base is the number of times `ACTIVITY` == 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor'

Name: Ratio of cases containing both 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' and 'Completed + In Call' to cases containing only 'Completed + In Call'
Metric: Percentage of 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' out of all 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Average position (step number) of 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' within its process variants
Metric: the average of the number of times `ACTIVITY` == 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor'

Name: Percentage of 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' occurrences in high-duration variants (performance > median variant duration)
Metric: Percentage of 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' out of all cases

Name: Number of times 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' is part of a rework loop (i.e., followed later by a repeated activity such as 'Accepted + In Progress')
Metric: Number of 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' activities for cases where activity 'Accepted + In Progress' occurs

Name: Percentage of 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' relative to the total count of wait-type activities in the VINST incident management process
Metric: Percentage of 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' out of all 'Accepted + Wait'

Name: Frequency of 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' in comparison to the combined frequency of all non-wait terminal activities like 'Completed + Cancelled' and 'Unmatched + Unmatched'
